---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Helicon Labs | Engineering Governance</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Helicon Labs builds engineering governance and automation products. Fleetu is in active MVP development."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Helicon Labs | Engineering Governance" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="We build systems to orchestrate engineering change at scale, with safety and auditability."
    />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://heliconlabs.dev" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.svg" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a1322" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="wrapper header">
        <p class="badge">System Status: Online</p>
        <h1 class="title">HELICON LABS</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Building practical systems for engineering governance and automation.
          MVP in active development, focused on scalable change orchestration with
          clear audit trails.
        </p>

        <article class="panel" aria-label="Helicon bootstrap terminal">
          <div class="panel-top">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="panel-title">Helicon Boot Console</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal">
            <p class="line l1">&gt; Initializing governance runtime...</p>
            <p class="line l2">
              &gt; Loading module: <strong>Fleetu</strong> (Engineering Governance)
            </p>
            <p class="line l3">
              &gt; Validating control-plane architecture: <strong>orchestrator-first</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="line l4">&gt; Establishing order in the software fleet.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <section class="grid" aria-label="company overview">
          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>What We Build</h3>
            <p>
              Products that help engineering teams ship organization-wide technical
              changes with predictable rollout, governance, and observability.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Current Status</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>SaaS multi-tenant architecture defined</li>
              <li>GitHub-first integration strategy in place</li>
              <li>MVP use case: dependency update orchestration</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Contact</h3>
            <p>
              hello@heliconlabs.dev
            </p>
            <p>
              Based in Brazil, building for global engineering organizations.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-8">
            <h3>Repository Hub</h3>
            <div class="repo-list">
              <a class="repo-link" href="https://github.com/HeliconLabs/fleetu-ideacao" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                fleetu-ideacao
                <small>Product vision, specs, and architecture decisions (ADR).</small>
              </a>
              <a class="repo-link" href="https://github.com/HeliconLabs/fleetu-app" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                fleetu-app
                <small>Application implementation (web, API, and shared contracts).</small>
              </a>
              <a class="repo-link" href="https://github.com/HeliconLabs/fleetu-infra" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                fleetu-infra
                <small>Infrastructure as code, environments, and operational baseline.</small>
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Why Helicon</h3>
            <p>
              Keep the control plane lean. Run execution in customer infrastructure.
              Scale through clear contracts instead of platform lock-in.
            </p>
          </article>
        </section>

        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary" href="https://github.com/HeliconLabs" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Open GitHub Org</a>
          <a class="btn" href="https://github.com/HeliconLabs/.github" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Org Profile</a>
        </div>

        <footer class="footer">Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Helicon Labs</footer>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
